Class TextComponentImpl

    • EObjectImpl

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Component, ReadableComponent, TextComponent

    public class TextComponentImpl
extends ReadableComponentImpl
implements TextComponent
    An implementation of the model object 'Text Component'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Descriptor
    • Width
    • Height
    • Date
    • Text Height
    • Text Map
